      "language": "english",
      "review": "The reason why I have such a large amount of playtime is because I've played since november\n\nA fantastic Windjammers-esque game that holds up on it's own! I've been playing this every day from January and it's great! Only 2 developers and still they managed to create a game that has just the right gameplay to be inviting to all, but while at the same time being able to give enough depth for a good competitive scene to arise.\n\nDo yourself a favor and get this one! I don't write reviews often, and when I do it's something really good.\n\nAs of March 7th the game is free on Playstation+ for one month So if you own a PS4 try it out there!",
