      "language": "english",
      "review": "SUCH a FUN game!\n\nInherently...\n\nIf you know ping pong, you'll know Disc Jam.\nIf you know Air Hockey, you'll know DJ.\nIf you know Tennis, you'll know DJ.\nIf you know STREET FIGHTER, you'll be right at home as well.\n\nThe timing, the different types of throws, the power ups, the tension...this is such a great game.  And at the price it's a MUST BUY.\n\nGreat job and Kudos to Jay and Tim!",
